reviewText: The reason why I like king diamond this dvd.

Not what I expected at all. Very poor picture quality, it was recorded from a foreign headbangers ball. Its a vhs to dvd transfer. Not satisfied.

I ordered this thinking it was a King Diamond DVD (as described). It was not, in fact, none of the songs or interviews that were on the back cover in writing were on the actual DVD. I enjoy Mercyful Fate (which was the DVD I received-a very bad copy of it) but I was ordering a King Diamond DVD. Very disappointed.
